    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey @joshuacheong! Currently I'm not sure about whether we'll be able to include native Solang support in Truffle, I can't speak for the entire team here but it would definitely have to be discussed. Something that you may find interesting, however, is that Truffle actually has some infrastructure for \"custom compiler setup\". It requires some manual tweaking but it seems like there may be a chance you'd find it useful. And, you know, I like helping people hack :)\r\n\r\nCheck out [this section of the Truffle docs on external compilers](https://trufflesuite.com/docs/truffle/reference/configuration/#external-compilers).",
